Class NormalizationPattern

java.lang.Object
  org.gvsig.normalization.patterns.NormalizationPattern
All Implemented Interfaces:
GeocodingPersistence
public class NormalizationPattern
extends java.lang.Object
implements GeocodingPersistence

Class Patternnormalization. This class is the normalization pattern. This pattern has your name (_patternname), your xml file path (_patternurl), the attribute (_nofirstrows) that says the number of the rows in the text file that will not be normalized and the list of elements (_elements) that make the pattern
